1486,"""allow_partial_update"" option does not work with resource lists of packages",seanh,seanh,"1. Call ckan.logic.action.update:package_update()
2. Pass in a context dict with ""allow_partial_update"":True
3. Pass in a partial data dict containing only the package's ID and those fields that you want to update (e.g. title).

=> All of the package's resource will have their statuses changed to ""deleted"".

The ""allow_partial_update"" option should apply to the resource lists of packages, but it does not.",defect,closed,minor,,ckan,fixed,,,ckan,none
